plot: Apu struggles with fatherhood after Manjula gives birth to octuplets.

Apu's wife Manjula gives birth to octuplets, making them celebrities and giving them free baby care goods - though these are withdrawn after a Shelbyville woman has nine babies. Exhausted by child care Apu allows showman Larry Kidkill to exhibit his children at the zoo but instantly regrets it and gets Homer to help him rescue them. Unfortunately they are caught and, in exchange for the babies' return, Homer must perform on a trick-cycle whilst being attacked by snakes.—don @ minifie-1
